@startuml
title Manual Analysis Tooling - Deployment / Runtime Diagram

node "Workspace Package" {
    artifact "analysis.yaml" as AnalysisYaml
    artifact "manual.lock" as CommittedLock
    artifact "results.json" as ResultsJson

    node "Context Providers" {
        artifact "filegroup inputs" as FilegroupInputs
        artifact "cc_library transitive\nsources + attrs" as CcInputs
    }

    component "manual_analysis\n(macro)" as Macro
    component "manual_analysis.update\n(executable target)" as UpdateTarget
    component "manual_analysis\n(test target)" as TestTarget
}

node "Bazel Action / Runfiles Layer" {
    artifact "file manifest TSV" as FileManifest
    artifact "rule manifest TSV" as RuleManifest
    artifact "computed_lock.txt" as ComputedLock

    component "manual_analysis_update_runner" as UpdateRunner
    component "interactive_runner_cli" as InteractiveRunner
    component "update_lock" as UpdateLock
    component "manual_analysis_test_runner" as TestRunner
}

node "User / Terminal Runtime" {
    component "_SplitPaneUI\n(prompt_toolkit)" as UI
}

node "Traceability Outputs" {
    artifact "name.lobster" as LobsterOutput
    component "LOBSTER tools" as LobsterTools
}

FilegroupInputs --> Macro : contexts
CcInputs --> Macro : contexts
AnalysisYaml --> Macro : analysis
CommittedLock --> Macro : lock_file
ResultsJson --> Macro : results_file

Macro --> UpdateTarget : expands to
Macro --> TestTarget : expands to

UpdateTarget --> FileManifest : create
UpdateTarget --> RuleManifest : create
UpdateTarget --> UpdateRunner : executable
UpdateRunner --> InteractiveRunner : run analysis
InteractiveRunner --> UI : render prompts
UpdateRunner --> UpdateLock : refresh lock
UpdateLock --> CommittedLock : rewrite

TestTarget --> FileManifest : create
TestTarget --> RuleManifest : create
FileManifest --> UpdateRunner : read
RuleManifest --> UpdateRunner : read
FileManifest --> TestRunner : read
RuleManifest --> TestRunner : read
TestTarget --> UpdateLock : compute sandbox lock
UpdateLock --> ComputedLock : write
TestTarget --> TestRunner : execute checks
TestRunner --> CommittedLock : compare
TestRunner --> ResultsJson : validate
TestRunner --> AnalysisYaml : load requirements
TestRunner --> LobsterOutput : emit
LobsterOutput --> LobsterTools : downstream input

@enduml

